headline.print_headline: Global Game Responds to Cries of 'Fore' With New Gimmicks
headline.main: Global Game Responds to Cries of 'Fore' With New Gimmicks

lead_paragraph: Tiger Woods is the world's top-earning athlete and tournaments still lure blue-chip sponsors and huge TV rights but golf is losing millions of players, prompting desperate ideas to stem the tide.
